{"tid":1000181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港外滙基金第四季虧損306億","createTime":"2019-01-29T09:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T00:18:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"70d96f48e853666d701d9b2bb57941b99b37d2fb","tid":1000181,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"金管局公佈，外滙基金去年投資收入139億元，較2017年的2,640億元大減94.7%。<br />\n<br />\n單計第四季，外滙基金虧損306億元。以本港人口744萬人計，單計第四季，每名港人於外滙基金蝕超過4,000元。<br />\n<br />\n去年第四季虧損額，屬2015年第3季以來新高，2015年第3季虧損近638億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190129/59199173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199173&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ff33b4bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199173&h=59b9efb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190129/59199173</a>"},{"pid":"21e85003a5dfe3dfcece8ca07cd6643d6e1d7be2","tid":1000181,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bf3079b1240fdeef021c59e47c4cc98e82381e","tid":1000181,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:06:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"993eeaed2bde9d773bcfb7d17fc08eb936fb7ff2","tid":1000181,"uid":39777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"拎哂去救國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f124e8d461c1ce7288bc41c40cdf46a62cffa959","tid":1000181,"uid":